Articles.Content:
It usually happens when I try to return to kerbin's base, or when I hit "Recover vessel"

 

I suspect some type of problem with the mods. But I can't figure our which is causing trouble since I don't understand the log files.

Any help would be appreciated. The link I shared has both the Player file in /LocalLow/Squad and the Crash folder said file redirects you at the end, the one in /Temp.
You should be a bit more careful about sharing these kinds of files. What i presume to be your first name is displayed at the very bottom of the error.log file.

30 minutes ago, Cattette said:

What i presume to be your first name is displayed at the very bottom of the error.log file.

That's a Windows username. If one is sensitive about one's name, one shouldn't use it as a username or login... But then why would one be, there are likely thousands of other people with the same. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯

Nuke that thing from orbit, then try again.
